{"tid":13514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢到有冇鼻竇炎既巴打","createTime":"2016-11-30T05:48:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T08:15:56.000Z","uid":12146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0db227cb6d50d01d077c1c1680424ea02cd26d","tid":13514,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經有左半年，食極抗生素都好唔到"},{"pid":"743afcf50ffd6fffb8dc58a47ed97fcd4f036c6c","tid":13514,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:51:44.000Z","msg":"做手術"},{"pid":"58be83b6285e5f5ddcaee9846907e68f22551dd1","tid":13514,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做手術</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有考慮過，巴打有試過？"},{"pid":"def380c887638640ed9c8f2d9ce7f5cb28df161e","tid":13514,"uid":25321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:12:58.000Z","msg":"有咩病徵"},{"pid":"4794edca742020656fc5646666b143f259732d1a","tid":13514,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩病徵</blockquote>上兩個星期食抗生素前有頭痛，好多痰，狂咳，食野冇味。食完幾日抗生素之後係剩返啲痰未清到，到琴日又開始食野冇味"},{"pid":"8d62e936c950e630397069a9091ec64cbad010b8","tid":13514,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9efaaeb5b51d0d1cf0c873ce6db7b56f0371611","tid":13514,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cdc0c9f906d5876f0c75e4cd5cb0c28a2b9592a","tid":13514,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:37:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520a69dca4788b5a88ac17026f03fc9ecba386d0","tid":13514,"uid":29128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T08:25:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做手術</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有考慮過，巴打有試過？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係近排照mri果時發現既 <br />\n本身冇理佢<br />\n但係呢排引埋鼻敏感 勁辛苦所以有諗過"},{"pid":"61e9f8fab710e094659dac65164165fe2c7c0a70","tid":13514,"uid":12146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37567959f8aecef5882e0f3db6834d72b01bbbd1","tid":13514,"uid":35630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:13:55.000Z","msg":"轉季病患 多數食藥冇事"},{"pid":"c37dd2c14bdd02cbc87ef4003ca499dd37300304","tid":13514,"uid":35630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩病徵</blockquote><br />\n鼻竇係 額頭同鼻翼兩側 鼻竇含膿 個頭烏低少少都頭痛"},{"pid":"6a640ca58644a784b4257196315a7cab4c5a1b31","tid":13514,"uid":35630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T08:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經有左半年，食極抗生素都好唔到</blockquote><br />\n如果半年都唔好你真係好嚴重下"}]}